&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3 months:&lt;/strong&gt; If you have stable income and good job security&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 months:&lt;/strong&gt; If you&amp;rsquo;re self-employed or have variable income&lt;/li&gt;
